 technology for emerging organic contaminants\ndegradation, since the combination of a low current density with the flow and\nmatrix induced disturbance increases and speeds up the compounds elimination in\na real environmental matrix.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2020 16:34:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-14"}
