epresented in the population. We use this approach to mimic\nfeatures of the Engage Study, an RDS sample of gay, bisexual and other men who\nhave sex with men in Montreal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2020 21:55:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2020 22:16:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
