 the four oxygen atoms. In addition, we explained\nthe reason for spin leaking down to the Ag layers. Mn on MgO/Ag does not show\nany spin-flip behavior in the STM, an unusual phenomenon, and we used our first\nprinciples-based approach to explain this unique observation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2020 05:28:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-17"}
